{"tid":1780223,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"以前有位阿姐話我知佢點樣迫走學校啲教畜","createTime":"2019-12-12T08:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T10:31:15.000Z","uid":262674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"64fb2f261fae633135eae13f6f015073e058039c","tid":1780223,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:04:46.000Z","msg":"真實例子，二手料啦算係<br />\n<br />\n十幾年前有位姐姐同我講佢既歷史<br />\n話佢十幾年前做中學生時（即係依家計成三十年前）<br />\n有位老師係好討厭教得又差又偏心又針對同學<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢地全班決定罷課坐禮堂要求校長炒左個老師<br />\n本身個校長係攬個老師，想勸佢地收皮，否則後果自負<br />\n點知全級一齊加入（佢話全部人都好憎果個教畜）<br />\n罷左成個星期課之後<br />\n該教畜以「私人理由」辭職<br />\n<br />\n我當時聽到係驚訝既<br />\n我係乖學生，無諗過係可以咁做<br />\n跟住佢答番我：點解唔得，唔啱就要屌<br />\n<br />\n你諗下<br />\n人地三十年前都行得咁前呀<br />\n你地都可以咁做<br />\n迫教畜迫仆街校長走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知對大家有無幫助 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢無提過佢係邊間中學<br />\n只係講係 BAND 5"},{"pid":"1e7a934a398c827b52d1358810301b2b551d5235","tid":1780223,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:08:32.000Z","msg":"你間濕9學校點同成個香港比<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4811bde701206db2410d9202b9998fbf6e9f744b","tid":1780223,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:13:18.000Z","msg":"你全校6分1人 但係香港7分2人出黎  都係唔會應 點逼"},{"pid":"c552a2c29dfe6ace7aff5fde27283646ecef03cc","tid":1780223,"uid":300165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e7a934a398c827b52d1358810301b2b551d5235","tid":1780223,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:08:32.000Z","msg":"你間濕9學校點同成個香港比<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:14:25.000Z","msg":"對付學校班藍絲教畜"},{"pid":"f005eb0126a47cef9b2026efb8eed1d393ab5804","tid":1780223,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:29:32.000Z","msg":"Band 5一早打到個教畜唔敢翻工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁溫和嘅做法真係算好乖"},{"pid":"480706d3ce8fd615fc888f6a53c9f47f4db54e37","tid":1780223,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e7a934a398c827b52d1358810301b2b551d5235","tid":1780223,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:08:32.000Z","msg":"你間濕9學校點同成個香港比<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:28:50.000Z","msg":"係用黎對付啲藍教畜<br />\n<br />\n唔係成個香港咁諗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff736579863cd19af79b746e6a42a21ebdfb0bf","tid":1780223,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f005eb0126a47cef9b2026efb8eed1d393ab5804","tid":1780223,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:29:32.000Z","msg":"Band 5一早打到個教畜唔敢翻工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁溫和嘅做法真係算好乖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:31:15.000Z","msg":"我仲有個例子呀<br />\nBAND 1 架<br />\n九龍喇沙既朋友<br />\n佢話如果啲老師廢<br />\n一入課室係會畀全班人掉野或者鬧<br />\n有時要喊住出門口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果藍教畜係學校入面變過街老鼠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇佢點教落去"}]}